<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:15:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着中国刺激措施的消退，伦敦股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/london-stocks-fall-china-stimulus-boost-fades-2024-09-25/</link><description>英国股市周三下跌，回吐前一交易日涨幅，因投资者质疑对中国广泛刺激措施的乐观情绪是否过度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 07:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/london-stocks-fall-china-stimulus-boost-fades-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国推动的涨势失去动力，欧洲股市持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-slip-china-fuelled-rally-loses-steam-2024-09-25/</link><description>尽管中国刺激计划刺激的涨势出现放缓迹象，但在基本资源上涨的支撑下，周三欧洲股市收复了部分跌幅。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 07:26:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-slip-china-fuelled-rally-loses-steam-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔卡拉斯希望戴维斯杯不会成为纳达尔的“最后一支舞”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-hopes-davis-cup-will-not-be-nadals-last-dance-2024-09-25/</link><description>卡洛斯·阿尔卡拉斯对拉法·纳达尔加入西班牙戴维斯杯队参加11月四分之一决赛表示欢迎，并希望马拉加的比赛不会标志着这位22届大满贯冠军职业生涯的结束。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-hopes-davis-cup-will-not-be-nadals-last-dance-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国呼吁老年志愿者促进经济发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-calls-elderly-volunteers-boost-economy-development-2024-09-25/</link><description>中国正在敦促其迅速老龄化的人口自愿参加社区服务，帮助一些地区的发展努力，并在教育和体育等领域做出贡献，因为当局试图支撑日益萎缩的劳动力队伍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-calls-elderly-volunteers-boost-economy-development-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称其飞机在巡逻时被中国海军直升机跟踪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-its-aircraft-was-shadowed-by-chinese-navy-helicopter-during-2024-09-25/</link><description>菲律宾周三表示，其渔业局飞机在有争议的黄岩岛附近巡逻时，遭到一架中国海军直升机的跟踪和接近，这是两国在领土问题上陷入激烈争执的另一场对峙。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-its-aircraft-was-shadowed-by-chinese-navy-helicopter-during-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官表示星展银行将把中国证券合资公司的股权提高到91%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/dbs-moving-raise-china-securities-joint-venture-stake-91-ceo-says-2024-09-25/</link><description>星展集团首席执行官皮尤什·古普塔 (Piyush Gupta) 周三表示，该集团正在将其在中国证券合资企业的所有权从 51% 增加到 91%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/dbs-moving-raise-china-securities-joint-venture-stake-91-ceo-says-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国新刺激计划引起全球市场轰动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-new-stimulus-plans-make-splash-global-markets-2024-09-25/</link><description>在北京宣布自疫情大流行以来最大规模的刺激措施后，中国敞口资产周二大幅上涨，以期使世界第二大经济体摆脱今年震动全球货币和股市的通缩恐慌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-new-stimulus-plans-make-splash-global-markets-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国的货币政策忽视了对经济增长的关键威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-monetary-volleys-miss-key-threat-economic-growth-2024-09-25/</link><description>中国央行已转向更为激进的宽松立场，但其政策武器并未将经济增长的主要敌人：持续疲软的消费者需求纳入考虑范围。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:56:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-monetary-volleys-miss-key-threat-economic-growth-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>印尼称赞中国公司为陷入困境的新资本的首个外国投资者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-hails-chinese-firm-first-foreign-investor-troubled-new-capital-2024-09-25/</link><description>周三，印尼总统佐科·维多多(Joko Widodo)在这个东南亚国家陷入困境的婆罗洲岛新首都为一家中国公司的房地产综合体破土动工，并称赞这是一项吸引其他国家的开拓性外国投资。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:43:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-hails-chinese-firm-first-foreign-investor-troubled-new-capital-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>泰国汽车业因订单下降和家庭债务飙升而举步维艰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/thai-auto-sector-reels-falling-orders-soaring-household-debt-2024-09-25/</link><description>泰国价值 530 亿美元的汽车工业正面临严峻的未来，因为负债累累的国内消费者难以筹集购买资金，而其主要传统汽车的海外买家越来越多地转向电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:16:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/thai-auto-sector-reels-falling-orders-soaring-household-debt-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车劳资冲突凸显欧洲汽车工厂难题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-labour-clash-spotlights-europes-car-factory-conundrum-2024-09-25/</link><description>路透社对欧洲六家汽车制造商的工厂产能利用率数据进行的审查显示，大众汽车并不是一个例外。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-labour-clash-spotlights-europes-car-factory-conundrum-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国刺激制糖热潮之后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-25/</link><description>凯文·巴克兰 (Kevin Buckland) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 04:34:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚财长本周将访问中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-treasurer-travel-china-this-week-2024-09-25/</link><description>澳大利亚财长吉姆·查尔默斯表示，他将于本周前往中国与中国同行举行会谈，这是澳大利亚财长七年来首次进行此类访问。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 03:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-treasurer-travel-china-this-week-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市因刺激措施反弹而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-25/</link><description>周三全球股市下跌，其中中国刺激措施持续推动的反弹成为一大亮点，而美元则承压，原油从数周高位回落。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:51:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国解放军罕见公开试射洲际弹道导弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-pla-launches-intercontinental-ballistic-missile-into-pacific-ocean-2024-09-25/</link><description>中国周三表示，已成功向太平洋发射了罕见的洲际弹道导弹，此举可能会引发国际社会对中国核建设的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:17:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-pla-launches-intercontinental-ballistic-missile-into-pacific-ocean-2024-09-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>